```plantuml
@startuml tarhses_esp-alarm-clock

actor User

participant "main.c" as Main
participant "alarm.c" as Alarm
participant "network.c" as Network
participant "display.c" as Display
participant "sound.c" as Sound
participant "pot.c" as Potentiometer
participant "storage.c" as Storage

User -> Main: Power On
Main -> Storage: Initialize Storage
Storage -> Main: Storage Initialized

Main -> Network: Initialize WiFi & Sync Time
Network -> Main: WiFi Connected & Time Synced

Main -> Potentiometer: Read Potentiometer Values
Potentiometer -> Main: Alarm Time Set

User -> Alarm: Activate Alarm
Alarm -> Main: Alarm Activated

Main -> Display: Update Display with Time & Alarm Status
Display -> Main: Display Updated

Alarm -> Sound: Trigger Alarm Sound
Sound -> Storage: Fetch Audio File
Storage -> Sound: Audio File Fetched
Sound -> Sound: Play Audio

User -> Alarm: Snooze/Stop Alarm
Alarm -> Sound: Stop Sound
Sound -> Alarm: Sound Stopped

Main -> Network: Monitor WiFi Connection
Network -> Main: Reconnect if Needed

@enduml
```